&lt;p&gt;This role reports to the Sr. IT Manager and is part of the Desktop Support team responsible for supporting 300+ staff members. In this position, you’ll partner closely with our Systems Administration team and collaborate cross-departmentally to deliver solutions that support the broader goals of the organization. To thrive in this role, you’ll need to be a fast learner who works well both asynchronously and collaboratively in a remote-first environment.&lt;/p&gt;
