&lt;p&gt;As an Engineering Manager, you will lead the &lt;strong&gt;Authentication, Authorization, and Access Control (AAA)&lt;/strong&gt; team within ActBlue’s growing product engineering department. ActBlue processes millions in contributions a day for thousands of campaigns and organizations; the AAA team builds the features that let donors, campaigns, and staff log in, manage their accounts, and move through ActBlue&#39;s product suite seamlessly — while making sure the right people have access to the right things.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Engineering teams are charged with operating autonomously while maintaining alignment with the organization&#39;s objectives. In this role, you will support this charge by working with your team&#39;s engineers, Product Manager, and UX lead to determine strategic technical and product direction in line with organizational goals, foster transparency and engagement, and ensure successful cross-team communication and collaboration.&lt;/p&gt;
