&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3-5+ years of ERP platform management experience, including experience working with NetSuite ERP and Netsuite NSPB.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with payment processor, tax, and payroll integration with ERP&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A solid understanding of ERP systems, business processes, and reporting.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;NetSuite Administrator Certification (preferred)&lt;/li&gt;
